  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37268</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やった！　できたぁ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yay! We did it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしたの？　何かいいこと、あったの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's wrong? Did something good happen?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん！　ずっと書きためてたモンスター図鑑が
いっぱいになったんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yep! We've managed to gather a LOT of entries
in our monster compendium.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すごいや、&lt;Mel&gt;！　おめでとう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's pretty amazing, &lt;Mel&gt;! Congratulations!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがと♪　えへへ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehe...Thank you~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40408</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これで魔物の弱点が丸わかりだね！
これで楽になるよ！　大手柄だね！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now we know all the monsters' weaknesses!
It should make fighting them easier now. I commend you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えへへ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ehehe~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41832</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……苦労しないでも、ほとんどの魔物に
勝てるくらい強くなってるし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Easy or not...we've already grown strong enough
to win against any monster...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_192_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……喜んでっから、言わないけどな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Though, I figure that'd just sour the 
mood so I'll just not say it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
